Class DBACluster.AntHill.Cluster

  • java.lang.Object
    • weka.clusterers.DBACluster.AntHill.Cluster

    DBACluster.AntHill

    protected class DBACluster.AntHill.Cluster
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<DBACluster.AntHill.InstancePlaceholder>
    This is the cluster that can be assigned to the instances in the dataset.

    It must not perform actions by itself, but is only used by other classes.
